## iOS Philosophy

This is the **focused** version. Core functionality optimised for mobile context:

- **Small screen** (6.1-6.9" phone) → show less, disclose progressively
- **Touch + gestures** → thumb-reachable, swipe-driven, haptic feedback
- **Siri & Shortcuts** → voice-first for common actions
- **Widgets & Live Activities** → glanceable info without opening the app
- **Intermittent use** → quick check, respond, leave

**Design rule:** If it takes more than 2 taps to do the most common task, redesign it. iOS users are one-handed on a train.

